    • calculateEventPopularity

      public void calculateEventPopularity()
      Calculate the event popularity based on the editions simulated. Calculates the occupancy rate of the event (participants per capacity) which is used by another method to return the popularity. This popularity is assigned to the event.
      See Also:
      • popularity
      • calculatePopularity(double occupancyRate)

    • calculatePopularity

      public static Event.PopularityLevel calculatePopularity(double occupancyRate)

      Parameters:
